![Unlock Labs Feature Announcement: State of Unlock Interactive Report](https://storage.googleapis.com/papyrus_images/b24fc7aee5bb4d90402308bc036067df.png)

<p>The State of Unlock Interactive Report is an interactive exploration tool for visualizing key metrics across the Unlock Protocol network encompassing over a dozen different EVM chains. </p><p>The State of Unlock includes:</p><ul><li><p>Smart contract ("Lock") activity over time </p></li><li><p>NFT ("Key") minting activity over time</p></li><li><p>Gross Network Product ("GNP") volume of network value transactions</p></li></ul><p>Key updates in this feature release include interactivity enhancements to the graph displaying network activity over time, code refactoring for better maintenance, removal of unused code, and improvements in the network selector functionality. </p><p>Additionally, visual enhancements including clickable captions and tooltips were introduced to improve the user interface.</p><figure float="none" data-type="figure" class="img-center" style="max-width: null;"><img src="/images/blog/unlock-labs-feature-announcement--state-of-unlock-interactive-report/260e5621576722cdd34ec52b1c0dd60f.png" blurdataurl="data:image/png;base64," nextheight="876" nextwidth="2162" class="image-node embed"><figcaption htmlattributes="[object Object]" class="hide-figcaption"></figcaption></figure><p style="text-align: start">For more details, you can <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow ugc" class="dont-break-out" href="https://unlock-protocol.com/state">view the State of Unlock Interactive Report here</a>.</p>
